001package org.biopax.paxtools.impl.level3;
002
003import org.biopax.paxtools.model.level3.*;
004import org.biopax.paxtools.model.level3.Process;
005import org.biopax.paxtools.util.BPCollections;
006
007import java.util.Set;
008
009
010public class PathwayStepImpl extends L3ElementImpl implements PathwayStep
011{
012        private Set<Process> stepProcess;
013        private Set<PathwayStep> nextStep;
014        private Set<PathwayStep> nextStepOf;
015        private Pathway pathwayOrderOf;
016        private Set<Evidence> evidence;
017
018        /**
019         * Constructor.
020         */
021        public PathwayStepImpl()
022        {
023                this.nextStep = BPCollections.I.createSafeSet();
024                this.nextStepOf = BPCollections.I.createSafeSet();
025                this.stepProcess = BPCollections.I.createSafeSet();
026                this.evidence = BPCollections.I.createSafeSet();
027        }
028
029        public Class<? extends PathwayStep> getModelInterface()
030        {
031                return PathwayStep.class;
032        }
033
034        public Set<PathwayStep> getNextStep()
035        {
036                return nextStep;
037        }
038
039        public void addNextStep(PathwayStep nextStep)
040        {
041                if (nextStep != null) {
042                        this.nextStep.add(nextStep);
043                        nextStep.getNextStepOf().add(this);
044                }
045        }
046
047        public void removeNextStep(PathwayStep nextStep)
048        {
049                if (nextStep != null) {
050                        nextStep.getNextStepOf().remove(this);
051                        this.nextStep.remove(nextStep);
052                }
053        }
054
055        public Set<PathwayStep> getNextStepOf()
056        {
057                return nextStepOf;
058        }
059
060        public Set<Process> getStepProcess()
061        {
062                return stepProcess;
063        }
064
065        public void addStepProcess(Process processStep)
066        {
067                if (processStep != null) {
068                        
069                        this.stepProcess.add(processStep);
070                        processStep.getStepProcessOf().add(this);
071                }
072        }
073
074        public void removeStepProcess(Process processStep)
075        {
076                if (processStep != null) {
077                        processStep.getStepProcessOf().remove(this);
078                        this.stepProcess.remove(processStep);
079                }
080        }
081
082        public Set<Evidence> getEvidence()
083        {
084                return evidence;
085        }
086
087        public void addEvidence(Evidence evidence)
088        {
089                if (evidence != null)
090                        this.evidence.add(evidence);
091        }
092
093        public void removeEvidence(Evidence evidence)
094        {
095                if (evidence != null)
096                        this.evidence.remove(evidence);
097        }
098
099        public Pathway getPathwayOrderOf()
100        {
101                return this.pathwayOrderOf;
102        }
103
104        protected void setPathwayOrderOf(Pathway pathwayOrderOf)
105        {
106                this.pathwayOrderOf = pathwayOrderOf;
107        }
108}
